title: Favourite new jungle routes in S5?

replies.body: Do you guys reckon it's always mandatory or very highly recommended to END at Red now for the Health back on Smite?
TBH not really, ganking a lane on under half hp isn't too bad but you have to know your limits and roughly how much damage the enemy laner can do and keep in mind the possibility of a counter gank.
Starting at golems, OR stack boxes at blue, then get team to leash u gromp (smite), then get blue.
Starting toad or red (preferably opponents jungle).
My jungle routes are basically the same. Just with different start points situationally.
